section.product--superscript#superscript
  .content
    img.product-icon src="/images/superscript-icon.png" alt="Superscript icon" width="64"
    h2.product-title.product-title--superscript Superscript
    p.product-summary The humble, lovable, secretly powerful comic book script editor for Mac and Windows
    p Superscript is the only text editor designed exclusively for writing scripts for comic books and graphic novels. This humble, unassuming app is loaded with features:
    ul
      li Automatically formats your script as you type
      li Automatically numbers panels & pages (even multi-page splashes!)
      li Spoken word count per dialog bubble, panel and page
      li Customizable spell check and auto-completion
      li Insert images and comments
      li Online collaboration (available late 2018)
      li Supports MacOS 10.9+ and Windows 7+
    p.product-links
      a.product-link.kickstarter-link href="http://superscriptapp.com"
        | Back us now on
        img src="/images/kickstarter.png" width="300"
      img src="/images/charon-comics.png" width="200"
      img src="/images/featured_kickstarter_comixcentral_badge-transparent-bkg.png" alt="ComixCentral Featured Kickstarter" width="200"
  img.superscript-screenshot src="/images/superscript-screenshot.png" alt="Superscript screenshot"
